  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA24">
<l>avaṉkaṇṭāy naṉṉeñcē yāraruḷuṅ kēṭu</l>
<l>mavaṉkaṇṭā yaimpulaṉāy niṉṟā – ṉavaṉkaṇṭāy</l>
<l>kāṟṟuttī nīrvāṉ karuvaraimaṇ kārōtac</l>
<l>cīṟṟattī yāvāṉuñ ceṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look at him, good heart: rare grace and loss</l>
<l>he [is]. Look, he stands as the five senses. Look,</l>
<l>wind, fire, water, sky, black mountain, earth, the rain flood,</l>
<l>the fire of anger he becomes, too, in turn.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
